{\pard \s2 \f1\fs28\ql\sb240\sa180\i\b {\*\bkmkstart codeblocksandfencedcodeblocks}{\*\bkmkend codeblocksandfencedcodeblocks}Code Blocks and Fenced Code Blocks\par}

{\pard \s0 \qj\sa180\f0\fs24 Code blocks and Fenced Code Blocks are implemented using the LaTeX \'93Listings\'94 package. Basic settings for listing are used and you can \'93tweak\'94 those (such as including line numbers) by opening the  of the inset in LyX and making changes in the dialog box.
